{"tid":2094122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動Post］今個星期淨係做好兩件事","createTime":"2020-07-04T10:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:28:52.000Z","uid":239499,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ed033ef8ba874d8f8357ef9fe2e4633dd6188d","tid":2094122,"uid":239499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行動一：支持本土電影</span><br />\n<br />\n係捍衛香港嘅民族性上，支持本土文化係十分重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，懇請你係今個星期得閒嘅時候就入場支持本土電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErW7s2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErW7s2S.jpg&h=c5ae2b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oND5Y9x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoND5Y9x.jpg&h=1ae228e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k3F8cuy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk3F8cuy.jpg&h=52e48ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃藍&mdash;-戲院篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790760</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行動二：宣傳立法會初選</span><br />\n<br />\n每條戰線都要打，立法會35+都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次公投人數真心失望，所以今次唔好再係咁啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hq8cvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hq8cvg.png&h=80a8b516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得係投票之前睇返選舉論壇，唔好亂投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更多資訊可留意<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.thestandnews.com/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.thestandnews.com%2Fhome%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=ba16555c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.thestandnews.com%2Fhome%2F&h=e86e7927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.thestandnews.com/home/</a><br />\n<br />\n以上兩個行動風險可以話係極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以懇請你地幫手完成左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話：我想要返香港人日程呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"5a52849fa55b981f795d45ef7e5df18c56c2a81d","tid":2094122,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dee70e3c3bfedbd55618a72a94b90c704bffe33","tid":2094122,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b35e665a79a22717fb4959f6c8af51710fe70e","tid":2094122,"uid":239499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"40dd4d2af697d4e4d8dba810cbf06188cd0b09bc","tid":2094122,"uid":239499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f251d714b497c4664f5fea012acdff5be1d05b","tid":2094122,"uid":181308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" 